  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flashing Dark</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person horror game about a lighthouse keeper lately transferred to a new outpost. As he struggles to manage his work, he uncovers a dark and terrifying secret of the island he lives on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/87694fdd7fbe958651080021e0266ec1.poster.avif?t=1771410725\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/87694fdd7fbe958651080021e0266ec1.webm?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/87694fdd7fbe958651080021e0266ec1.mp4?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Gameplay</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is primarily a first-person narrative walking simulator with exploration, lighthouse routine simulation, and conversation mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/b80264eb674fd0d67d5130ded844938d.poster.avif?t=1771410725\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/b80264eb674fd0d67d5130ded844938d.webm?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/b80264eb674fd0d67d5130ded844938d.mp4?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS film aesthetic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NPCs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lighthouse keeper gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/ece399c176900014f597aea7935eec3e.poster.avif?t=1771410725\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/ece399c176900014f597aea7935eec3e.webm?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/ece399c176900014f597aea7935eec3e.mp4?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plot Intro</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game begins with Dave waking up on a train. Recently he has applied for a position of lighthouse keeper on a remote island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Dave arrives on the island, he is immediately struck by its eerie atmosphere. The lighthouse is old and dilapidated, and the surrounding forest is dark and foreboding. Dave soon finds something on the island that moves the story forward.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Flashing Dark</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >First-person horror game about a lighthouse keeper lately transferred to a new outpost. As he struggles to manage his work, he uncovers a dark and terrifying secret of the island he lives on.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/87694fdd7fbe958651080021e0266ec1.poster.avif?t=1771410725\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/87694fdd7fbe958651080021e0266ec1.webm?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/87694fdd7fbe958651080021e0266ec1.mp4?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Gameplay</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is primarily a first-person narrative walking simulator with exploration, lighthouse routine simulation, and conversation mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/b80264eb674fd0d67d5130ded844938d.poster.avif?t=1771410725\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/b80264eb674fd0d67d5130ded844938d.webm?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/b80264eb674fd0d67d5130ded844938d.mp4?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Atmospheric environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VHS film aesthetic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NPCs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Story.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lighthouse keeper gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/ece399c176900014f597aea7935eec3e.poster.avif?t=1771410725\" width=650 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/ece399c176900014f597aea7935eec3e.webm?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2838490/extras/ece399c176900014f597aea7935eec3e.mp4?t=1771410725\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plot Intro</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game begins with Dave waking up on a train. Recently he has applied for a position of lighthouse keeper on a remote island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When Dave arrives on the island, he is immediately struck by its eerie atmosphere. The lighthouse is old and dilapidated, and the surrounding forest is dark and foreboding. Dave soon finds something on the island that moves the story forward.</p>",
